on authority to reduce\n","   investor risk perception.\n","\n","2. Non-Oil Growth: Shift giga-project spending toward\n","   SME supply-chain integration to broaden the non-oil\n","   productive base beyond flagship developments.\n","\n","3. Saudization: Current Nitaqat quotas incentivise\n","   box-ticking over genuine skill transfer. Introduce\n","   productivity-linked Saudization credits tied to\n","   training certification outcomes.\n","\n","DATA CAVEATS\n","────────────\n","• Non-oil GDP figures for 2017–2021 use World Bank approximation\n","  (total GDP growth minus oil rents change). GASTAT overrides\n","  applied for 2022–2024.\n","• Saudization figures compiled from GASTAT/MHRSD press releases —\n","  not a continuous official time series.\n","• FDI data from World Bank WDI; may lag actual inflows by 1–2 years.\n","\n","━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n","Analysis produced using Python (pandas, matplotlib) + Claude AI.\n","Data: World Bank WDI, GASTAT, MHRSD. Author: Mor Wagan, MA Economics.\n","━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n","\n"]}]}]}